---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="House Painters Kingston | New Builds & Interior Repaints"
  description="House painters in Kingston — newer estates and 1980s homes, full interior repaints, new-build and renovation painting across Kingborough. Low-VOC paints, fixed quotes. Free estimate."
  canonical="https://hobarthousepainters.com.au/kingston/">

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <span class="hero-eyebrow">Kingston &middot; Blackmans Bay &middot; Kingston Beach &middot; Margate</span>
      <h1>House painters in <span class="accent">Kingston</span>.</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">
        Kingston and the Kingborough coast are growth country &mdash; a mix of
        newer estates, 1980s&ndash;90s family homes and a steady stream of
        renovations and new builds. From a full interior repaint to a brand-new
        home that needs its first proper colour, we work to a fixed quote and a
        clean, on-time finish.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a class="ph-cta btn btn-primary" href="/quote/" aria-label="Call us"><span aria-hidden="true">&#9742;</span> <span class="ph-text">Tap to call</span></a>
        <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/quote/">Get a free quote</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <span class="section-eyebrow">Why Kingston</span>
      <h2>Painting Kingston homes.</h2>
      <div class="divider"></div>
      <div style="max-width: 65rem;">
        <h3>1980s&ndash;90s homes due for their first big repaint.</h3>
        <p>
          A large slice of Kingston is 1980s&ndash;90s brick-veneer and timber
          family homes &mdash; many now on their original or first repaint and
          well overdue for a refresh. Builder-grade interiors from that era look
          dated fast, and exterior trim, eaves and fascia take a beating in the
          damp climate. A full interior repaint in a current colour, or an
          exterior refresh with proper prep, brings these homes right back to
          life. See <a href="/services/interior-painting/">interior house
          painting</a> and <a href="/services/exterior-painting/">exterior house
          painting</a>.
        </p>

        <h3 style="margin-top: 2rem;">New builds and renovations.</h3>
        <p>
          Kingborough keeps growing, and new builds and extensions need painting
          out properly &mdash; not rushed. New plasterboard needs the right
          sealer/undercoat before topcoats, new timber and trim need priming, and
          a renovation has to be blended seamlessly into the existing finishes.
          We coordinate around your builder&rsquo;s timeline, use low-VOC paints
          so a new home is healthy to move into, and leave a crisp, even finish
          throughout.
        </p>

        <h3 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Coastal exposure at Kingston Beach and Blackmans Bay.</h3>
        <p>
          Homes closer to Kingston Beach, Blackmans Bay and the water cop more
          salt air and weather on their exteriors. That shortens the repaint
          cycle and makes preparation &mdash; wash, mould treatment, priming bare
          timber &mdash; and the right coastal-rated paints even more important.
          We factor the exposure into the spec so the finish lasts.
        </p>

        <h3 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Family homes &mdash; low-VOC, low disruption.</h3>
        <p>
          Kingston is family suburb, and we get asked about paint fumes and
          turnaround all the time. We use low- and zero-VOC interior paints as
          standard for faster, healthier re-occupancy, stage rooms so you keep
          using the house, and protect floors and furniture carefully throughout.
        </p>

        <h3 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Typical Kingston jobs.</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Full interior repaint of a 1990s family home in a current scheme</li>
          <li>New-build paint-out coordinated with the builder&rsquo;s handover</li>
          <li>Renovation and extension painting blended into existing finishes</li>
          <li>Coastal exterior repaint at Kingston Beach or Blackmans Bay</li>
          <li>Roof clean and recoat to refresh a tired tile or metal roof</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <h2>Other service areas.</h2>
      <div class="areas-grid">
        <a class="area-pill" href="/sandy-bay/">Sandy Bay</a>
        <a class="area-pill" href="/glenorchy/">Glenorchy</a>
        <a class="area-pill" href="/moonah/">Moonah</a>
        <a class="area-pill" href="/new-town/">New Town</a>
        <a class="area-pill" href="/hobart-region/">All Greater Hobart</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="cta-block">
        <h2>Free Kingston painting quote.</h2>
        <p>Interior repaints, new builds and renovations. Low-VOC paints, fixed price, clean finish.</p>
        <div class="hero-actions" style="justify-content:center;">
          <a class="ph-cta btn btn-primary" href="/quote/" aria-label="Call us"><span aria-hidden="true">&#9742;</span> <span class="ph-text">Tap to call</span></a>
          <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/quote/">Book online</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
